'''Tallaga Garrison''' was a [[Garrison/Legends|garrison]] located in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Tallaga]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sucharme]]. The garrison contained one wing of [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], led by [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Veril Acamma]].

The [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] shut down the Tallaga Garrison in an attempt to prevent armed resistance after the Federation's occupation of the planet.

